metadata.name: SPACETOWER 01
metadata.description:
"WHAT IF?"
You could stroll through different planets, all in the comforts of your own luxurious home.

A multi-terrain mobile apartment, capable of zipping through jungles.
Equipped with multidirectional gyro capabilities.

It's no longer a question of 'what if' anymore, but WHEN.

This is for the space voyager, the connoisseur, the affluent, with the ambition to rise above others, and the humility to stay grounded.

6 floors - 12,000 sqft / 1,114 sqm of opulence, with a roof top pool

This is the future, nodding to the past.

Syarawi Architect -
